{#
  Parameters:
    - "extra_classes" (string) (default: '')
    - "extra_attributes" (array) (default: []): format: [
        {
          "name" (string) (default: ''),
          "value" (string) (default: '')
        },
        ...
      ]
#}

{# Internal properties #}

{% set _css_class = 'ecl-accordion' %}
{% set _extra_attributes = '' %}

{# Internal logic - Process properties #}

{% if extra_classes is defined and extra_classes is not empty %}
  {% set _css_class = _css_class ~ ' ' ~ extra_classes %}
{% endif %}

{% if extra_attributes is defined and extra_attributes is not empty and extra_attributes is iterable %}
  {% for attr in extra_attributes %}
    {% set _extra_attributes = _extra_attributes ~ ' ' ~ attr.name ~ '="' ~ attr.value ~ '"' %}
  {% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{# Print the result #}

<dl class="{{ _css_class }}"{{ _extra_attributes|raw }} data-ecl-accordion="true" role="presentation">
  <dt role="heading" aria-level="3">
    <button
      data-ecl-accordion-toggle="true" aria-controls="accordion-example-content" type="button" class="ecl-accordion__toggle ecl-button ecl-button--ghost">
      <span
        class="ecl-button__container">
        <svg focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" data-ecl-icon="true" class="ecl-button__icon ecl-button__icon--before ecl-icon ecl-icon--s">
          <use xlink:href="/static/media/icons.cbfd6efe.svg#general--digital"></use>
        </svg>
        <span class="ecl-button__label" data-ecl-label="true">Delivery of last pending proposals, a common
        Destiny of unity, the hour of European Democracy</span>
      </span>
    </button>
  </dt>
  <dd class="ecl-accordion__content" id="accordion-example-content" hidden="" role="region">The College of
    Commissioners held today the first weekly meeting of 2019 which was devoted to discussing the challenges of this
    new year. Commissioners used the opportunity to take stock and discuss the year ahead, including the European
    elections in May and other important milestones ahead.
  </dd>
  <dt role="heading" aria-level="3">
    <button
      data-ecl-accordion-toggle="true" aria-controls="accordion-example2-content" type="button" class="ecl-accordion__toggle ecl-button ecl-button--ghost">
      <span
        class="ecl-button__container">
        <svg focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" data-ecl-icon="true" class="ecl-button__icon ecl-button__icon--before ecl-icon ecl-icon--s">
          <use xlink:href="/static/media/icons.cbfd6efe.svg#general--energy"></use>
        </svg>
        <span class="ecl-button__label" data-ecl-label="true">Energy union and climate</span>
      </span>
    </button>
  </dt>
  <dd class="ecl-accordion__content" id="accordion-example2-content" hidden="" role="region">A balanced and progressive
    trade policy to harness globalisation
  </dd>
  <dt role="heading" aria-level="3">
    <button data-ecl-accordion-toggle="true"
      aria-controls="accordion-example3-content" type="button" class="ecl-accordion__toggle ecl-button ecl-button--ghost">
      <span
        class="ecl-button__container">
        <svg focusable="false" aria-hidden="true" data-ecl-icon="true" class="ecl-button__icon ecl-button__icon--before ecl-icon ecl-icon--s">
          <use xlink:href="/static/media/icons.cbfd6efe.svg#general--regulation"></use>
        </svg>
        <span class="ecl-button__label" data-ecl-label="true">Delivery of last pending proposals, a common
        Destiny of unity, the hour of European Democracy</span>
      </span>
    </button>
  </dt>
  <dd class="ecl-accordion__content" id="accordion-example3-content" hidden="" role="region">In the modern global
    economy trade is essential for growth, jobs and competiveness, and the EU is committed to maintaining an open and
    rules-based trading system. With the rising threat of protectionism and weakened commitment of large players to
    global trade governance, the EU must take the lead.
  </dd>
</dl>